    "body": "@bobylito The base screenshots is computed from the git history. We use the **forking commit** between the pull-request commit and the pull-request target commit. Does that make sense?\r\nIt's the same logic as: https://percy.io/docs/learn/baseline-picking-logic#pull-requests\r\nWe have a load of unit-tests for it. I can link you them if you want.\r\n\r\nI agree, we need to document it!",
